<br>
Here is the general thrust of it:<br>
<br>
Sleeper awakes kills everyone.<br>
Warders no longer spawn.<br>
Other mobs now drop primal BUT drop predominately 2hs and less of it.  (Balance, easier to get but takes longer to farm)<br>
Very very very rarely dragon scales drop which may be turned in for gear. <p><B><I>Wyrdlan</i></b>@Rodcet Nife<BR><HR><BR><BR>
